data.description: Discover the potential of this 4bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home located in The  Vistas neighborhood. This property is a canvas waiting for your personal touch, with fantastic bones and endless possibilities. The spacious 3-car garage provides not only room for your vehicles but also additional storage space for all your toys and tools. Don't miss out on this opportunity to turn this house into your dream home. With its excellent location and potential, it's an investment in your future.
